            <title>[GROOVY-5416] Transform loaded by wrong class loader when @GroovyASTTransformationClass(classes = ...) is used</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-5416</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When @GroovyASTTransformationClass(classes = ...) is used, the transform will be loaded by CompilationUnit.classLoader rather than CompilationUnit.transformLoader. This may cause the transform not to work in environments (like Gradle) where transformLoader != classLoader.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Pull request will follow.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
